Package: pottR
Title: A Shared Collection of Utility Functions for Data Analysis and Reporting
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jason", "Pott", , "jasonpott+github@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "maintainer"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2068-0560"))
Description: Provides a collection of functions for summarizing data, formatting 'gt' tables,
    and calculating common descriptive statistics. These utilities support efficient and 
    reproducible workflows in data analysis and reporting.
